ED: Nararamdaman mo ba ang presensya?

01:15:23.640 --> 01:15:24.920
LORRAINE: Hindi, kabaligtaran lang.

01:15:25.120 --> 01:15:26.155
Wala akong nararamdaman.

01:15:27.640 --> 01:15:31.110
Maaaring tinitingnan natin
ang hysterical neurosis.

01:15:31.600 --> 01:15:33.875
Iyon ay magpapaliwanag
sa maraming personalidad

01:15:34.040 --> 01:15:35.473
